<L>__{exterior roadhouse later}
<A>__{sam walks outside. he stands in the red glow of neon light, looking toward the road... on the opposite side of which... ... sits a sorry little collection of whitewashed stucco bungalows, identified by a green neon sign as the glades motel. beyond the motel are the everglades, a great expanse of darkness. sam stares at the motel. at last he gets in his jeep. as he exits the lot, a second pair of headlights flashes on.}
